Sentencas: The present research focuses on a novel ceramic/glass composite seal.

Sentencas: The cycled seal was then characterized with a laser dilatometer to identify the glass transition, softening temperature, and thermal expansion properties.

Sentencas: High temperature ring-on-ring (RoR) experiments were performed to study the effect of glass transition and softening temperatures on mechanical response.
Titulo: Thermomechanical Properties of Cycled Ceramic/Glass Composite Seals for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: X-ray diffraction (XRD) techniques in conjunction with post-test micrographs were used to understand the observed mechanical response.
